		<td><a href="http://blog.cloudspokes.com"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/blogicon.png" width="55" style="padding-left:10px;padding-top:4px"></a></td>
		<td><a href="http://www.cloudspokes.com/challenges/feed"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/rss_icon.png" width="57" style="padding-left:10px;padding-top:3px"></a></td>
